00:00:55,250 --> 00:00:56,750
So many.

4
00:00:56,833 --> 00:00:58,041
So many days.

5
00:02:28,916 --> 00:02:30,000
[MIZOROGI]
Well, girls.

6
00:02:30,083 --> 00:02:31,791
I'm pleased to say
that the Annual Festival

