okay, Miss Tokaku.

22
00:03:17,458 --> 00:03:19,416
We just have to
stay strong, right?

23
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:21,291
Like Mr. Mizorogi said.

24
00:03:21,375 --> 00:03:23,458
[ISUKE]
Your blind optimism is pathetic.

25
00:03:23,541 --> 00:03:26,750
I can't stand it. Makes me
wanna smash your face.

26
00:03:26,833 --> 00:03:27,958
[TOKAKU grunts]

27
00:03:28,041 --> 00:03:30,250
[ISUKE] Ooh, I'm so scared!
[SUZU] Alright,

28
00:03:30,333 --> 00:03:32,541
[SUZU] calm down everybody!
[ISUKE] What?

29
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:34,125
[ISUKE]
Let's not fight over nothing.

30
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:36,458
We're just tense that's all.

31
00:03:36,541 --> 00:03:39,583
I think now's a good time
to take a little breather.

32
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:41,416
A breather?

33
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,541
[SUZU]
That's right.

34
00:03:42,625 --> 00:03:44,666
I stumbled upon
something wonderful.

35
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:48,916
So after class, what do you say
we all go and take a look?

36
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:54,750
[GIRLS giggling, gasping]

37
00:03:54,833 --> 00:03:56,916
[ISUKE] That's Myojo
Private School for you.

38
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,166
Even got their own water park!

39
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:02,791
[NIO] Duh! We've also got an
Olympic sized pool for classes.

40
00:04:02,875 --> 00:04:05,708
[SUZU] I had time reserved
exclusively for Class Black.

41
00:04:05,791 --> 00:04:08,708
After the festival, I think
we've earned a little R and R.

42
00:04:08,791 --> 00:04:10,000
Don't you?

43
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:12,750
And of course,
we have swimsuits too.

44
00:04:12,833 --> 00:04:14,833
Thank you so much!
It's incredible!

45
00:04:14,916 --> 00:04:17,125
C'mon Miss Tokaku,
let's go hurry up and change!

46
00:04:17,208 --> 00:04:20,333
[TOKAKU]
Uh... Hold on!

47
00:04:21,541 --> 00:04:25,291
Well. C'mon, ladies,
what are you waiting for?

48
00:04:28,708 --> 00:04:30,708
A school swimsuit?

49
00:04:30,791 --> 00:04:33,583
[SUMIREKO] Don't tell me they
expect us to wear that swimsuit.

50
00:04:33,666 --> 00:04:35,041
[ISUKE]
So lame.

51
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:37,541
They think we're just a bunch
of toddlers, don't they?

52
00:04:37,625 --> 00:04:40,416
If you're not a fan of the
school's designated swimwear,

53
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,833
well then, we have
more choices for you!

54
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:44,375
Pick whatever you like!

55
00:04:44,458 --> 00:04:47,208
Um, do you intend on
going scuba diving, Nio?

56
00:04:47,291 --> 00:04:50,875
[NIO] No way! I was going
for more of a bondage vibe!

57
00:04:50,958 --> 00:04:53,500
[SUMIREKO]
Okay. I've made my selection.

58
